37353>>>    // Add a DDO Structure 
37353>>>    //
37353>>>    // There is no need to synchronize a DD structure on the client so we do
37353>>>    // not set the Server property or send ADDOStructure. We will simply use
37353>>>    // DDO's to mine data and generate HTML for our cWebHTMLBox objects.
37353>>>    // It is the HTML in these objects that is sent to the client each time 
37353>>>    // this page is shown.
